g" alt="😅" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f483.png" alt="💃" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/Olympics?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#Olympics</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/Paris2024?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#Paris2024</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/BBCOlympics?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#BBCOlympics</a> <a href="https://t.co/MhRyszNeOa">pic.twitter.com/MhRyszNeOa</a></p><p> — BBC 体育 (@BBCSport) <a href="https://twitter.com/BBCSport/status/1822754278395498882?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 8 月 11 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>随后，艾利什在海滩救生员瞭望台上表演了《Birds Of A Feather》，之后史努比狗狗 (Snoop Dogg) 表演了《Drop It Like It&#39;s Hot》。史努比狗狗是今年法国首都奥运会上的杰出人物。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">比莉·艾利什 – 羽毛之鸟 – <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/OlympicGames?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#OlympicGames</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/Paris2024?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#Paris2024</a> <a href="https://t.co/sxpBbXgTwy">pic.twitter.com/sxpBbXgTwy</a></p><p> - QG Billie Eilish (@QGBillieEilish) <a href="https://twitter.com/QGBillieEilish/status/1822754028142440542?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 8 月 11 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>随后，他与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dr-dre">Dr. Dre</a>合作演绎了他们的经典热门歌曲“The Next Episiode”，结束了自己的表演。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="fr" dir="ltr"> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/CeremonieDeCloture?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#CeremonieDeCloture</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/SnoopDogg?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#SnoopDogg</a> ft <a href="https://twitter.com/h