-gaga">Lady Gaga</a>表演了法国歌舞歌曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-lady-gaga-perform-mon-truc-en-plumes-at-paris-olympics-opening-ceremony-3778447">《Mon truc enplumes》</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gojira">Gojira</a>表演了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-gojira-perform-ah-ca-ira-in-the-paris-olympics-opening-ceremony-3778455">法国大革命歌曲《Ah Ça Ira!》。</a>与歌剧歌手玛丽娜·维奥蒂。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/celine-dion">席琳·迪翁 (Celine Dion)</a>也是四年来首次演出，自<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/celine-dion-reveals-stiff-person-syndrome-diagnosis-reschedules-and-cancels-shows-3363354">2022 年透露自己被诊断出患有僵人综合症 (SPS) 以来，她在首场演出中演绎了伊迪丝·琵雅芙 (Edith Piaf) 的《L&#39;Hymne A L&#39;Amour》。</a></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-h-e-r-play-mission-impossible-theme-as-tom-cruise-performs-spectacular-stunt-at-paris-olympics-closing-ceremony-3782745">汤姆·克鲁斯在巴黎奥运会闭幕式上表演精彩特技，观看她演奏《碟中谍》主题曲的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
